 | l.4 α</p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Victoria Fendel, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive-simple-lemmatized\">  <div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <span data-text=\"Θεοῖς\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"θεός\">Θεοῖς</span>  <span data-text=\"Κατακθονίοις\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"καταχθόνιος\">Κατακθονίοις</span>  <span data-text=\"Ἰουλία\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Ἰουλία\">Ἰουλία</span>  <span data-text=\"Δομιτία\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"Δομιτία\">Δομιτία</span>  <span data-text=\"ἔζησεν\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"ζάω\">ἔζησεν</span>  <span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ἔτη</span>  <span data-text=\"ζ\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"ζ\">ζ</span>  <span data-text=\"μῆνας\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"μείς\">μῆνας</span>  <span data-text=\"γ\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"γ\">γ</span>  <span data-text=\"ἡμέρας\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"ἡμέρα\">ἡμέρας</span>  <span data-text=\"ε\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"ε\">ε</span>  <span data-text=\"Γονεῖς\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"Γονεῖς\">Γονεῖς</span>  <span data-text=\"ἐποίησαν\" data-n=\"65\" data-lemma=\"ποιέω\">ἐποίησαν</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-text=\"ΘΟεοῖς\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"θεός\">Ο</span><span data-text=\"Κατακθονίοις\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"καταχθόνιος\">Κ</span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἰουλία Δομιτία\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἰουλία\"><span data-text=\"Ἰουλία\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Ἰουλία\">ΙΟΥΛΙΑ</span></span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Δομιτία\"><span data-text=\"Δομιτία\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"Δομιτία\">ΔΟΜΙΤΙΑ</span></span></span><span data-text=\"ἔζησεν\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"ζάω\">ΕΖΗΣΕΝ</span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΕΤΗ</span><span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\"><span data-text=\"ζ\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"ζ\">Ζ</span></span><span data-text=\"μῆνας\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"μείς\">ΜΗΝΑΣ</span><span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\"><span data-text=\"γ\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"γ\">Γ</span></span><span data-text=\"ἡμέρας\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"ἡμέρα\">ΗΜΕΡΑΣ</span><span class=\"supraline\" title=\"line above\"><span data-text=\"ε\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"ε\">Ε</span></span><br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Γονεῖς\"><span data-text=\"Γονεῖς\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"Γονεῖς\">ΓΟΝΕΙΣ</span></span><span data-text=\"ἐποίησαλν\" data-n=\"65\" data-lemma=\"ποιέω\">ΕΠΟΙΗΣΛΝ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\">l.1 Θ | l.4 α</p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Victoria Fendel, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\"><div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><span data-text=\"Θεοῖς\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"θεός\">ΘΕΟΙΣ</span><span data-text=\"Κατακθονίοις\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"καταχθόνιος\">ΚΑΤΑΚΘΟΝΙΟΙΣ</span><span data-text=\"Ἰουλία\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Ἰουλία\">ΙΟΥΛΙΑ</span><span data-text=\"Δομιτία\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"Δομιτία\">ΔΟΜΙΤΙΑ</span><span data-text=\"ἔζησεν\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"ζάω\">ΕΖΗΣΕΝ</span><span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΕΤΗ</span><span data-text=\"ζ\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"ζ\">Ζ</span><span data-text=\"μῆνας\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"μείς\">ΜΗΝΑΣ</span><span data-text=\"γ\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"γ\">Γ</span><span data-text=\"ἡμέρας\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"ἡμέρα\">ΗΜΕΡΑΣ</span><span data-text=\"ε\" data-n=\"55\" data-lemma=\"ε\">Ε</span><span data-text=\"Γονεῖς\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"Γονεῖς\">ΓΟΝΕΙΣ</span><span data-text=\"ἐποίησαν\" data-n=\"65\" data-lemma=\"ποιέω\">ΕΠΟΙΗΣΑΝ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic001304_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001304_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001304.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001304-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text based on photographs</span>  </span>; </li><li><span class=\"line 1\">line.1: <span>lapis: Ο</span>  </span><br></li><li><span class=\"line 3\">line.3: <span>lapis: ΕΠΟΙΗΣΛΝ</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo</a></p>  <p>To the underworld spirits. Iulia Domitia lived for 7 years, 3 months, and 5 days. Her parents made this.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>Italian translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo</a></p>  <p>Agli Dei inferi. Giulia Domizia visse sette anni, tre mesi, cinque giorni. I suoi genitori realizzarono questo.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>The structure of the epitaph is the most common for pagan epitaphs, with the invocation to the underworld spirits, the name of the deceased in nominative and his/her age, the names of the dedicant (in this case, the parents, who are not named, see also IG 14.483 = <a href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001306\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001306</a>) and the dedication verb in the aorist form (Korhonen 2004: 85-86). The <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"la\">nomen</span>  <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Δομιτία</span> from the <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"la\">gens Domitia</span> may have spread especially since the reign of Nero: from prosopography and palaeography, therefore, the inscription can be dated from the mid-1st century CE to the end of the 2nd century CE.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Castelli 1769 151 no. 32 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084</a>  </li><li> Castelli 1784 159 no. 35 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083</a>  </li><li> Ferrara 1829 346 no. 2 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002005\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002005</a>  </li><li> Franz 1853 5704 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250</a>  </li><li> Kaibel 1890 <a href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">481</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</a>  </li><li> Korhonen 2004 98 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li> Korhonen 2004 85-86 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028</a>  </li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>Rhomboid Ο. The letters at l. 3 are slightly larger and more spaced out than the other lines.</p>  Lines 1-4  15-22  Interlineation line 1 to 2  not recorded  </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
